# 🧠 3. CHIP-BASED ROLE UI

Create reusable component:

```tsx
function FieldChip({ field, role, aggregation, onRemove }) {
  return (
    <div className="chip">
      <span>{field}</span>
      {aggregation && <span className="agg">({aggregation})</span>}
      <button onClick={onRemove}>×</button>
    </div>
  );
}
```

